 {"id":"bd-jhe7","title":"[AA][DPOR] Replay engine + divergence diagnostics","description":"## Goal
Implement replay validation: trace → schedule → execution, with mismatch diagnostics.

## Why
Replay is the backbone of debugging and proof‑carrying traces.

## Deliverables
- Replay driver with strict validation.
- Diff tool for divergence (first mismatched event).
